-- MOVES-Societe Generale names Americas corporate finance head
-- 
-- Wed Jun 25, 2014 02:10PM EDT
-- None



June 25 (Reuters) - Societe Generale Corporate & Investment Banking, a unit of French bank Societe Generale SA <SOGN.PA>, appointed Brian Thom as head of corporate finance for the Americas.

Thom will be based in New York and oversee mergers and acquisitions as well as equity capital markets.